OL,7,FA visually impaired artist from
OL,8,FCardiff has been commissioned to
OL,9,Fcreate a statue of her own guide dog,
OL,10,Fwhich will be showcased as part of an
OL,11,Fexhibition in London.
OL,13,FSian Healey was one of just 25 artists
OL,14,Ffrom across the UK selected by the
OL,15,Fcharity Guide Dogs, which supports
OL,16,Fblind and partially sighted
OL,17,Findividuals, to create a sculpture for
OL,18,Fa free art trail in London.
