OL,7,FThe artwork will be unveiled at Canary
OL,8,FWharf on 25 March as part of the 'Paws
OL,9,Fon the Wharf' project.JThe
OL,10,Finstallation will see a collection of
OL,11,Flarger-than-life guide dog sculptures
OL,12,Fto raise awareness and vital funds to
OL,13,Fhelp people with sight loss live more
OL,14,Factive and independent lives.
OL,16,FUri, Sian's own guide dog, was the
OL,17,Finspiration for her sculpture.
