OL,7,FSian, who has Albinism, a condition
OL,8,Fwhich affects her vision, said: "I
OL,9,Factually see things incredibly
OL,10,Fbrightly and strongly, almost like an
OL,11,Fimpressionist.
OL,13,F"I looked to Monet's work, and the
OL,14,Flater work of Turner, who both had
OL,15,Fsight conditions, and I began to adapt
OL,16,Fmy style to show my vision through art
OL,17,Fwork.
