OL,7,F"When I was thinking about the piece,
OL,8,FI thought 'how am I going to do
OL,9,Fthis?'. I went back to what was
OL,10,Fimportant to me, my guide dog."
OL,12,FWhen discussing the post card
OL,13,Fpaintings on the sculpture, she said:
OL,14,F"The things these guide dogs bring us
OL,15,Fis freedom and independence. That's
OL,16,Fwhere the idea of these post cards
OL,17,Fcame from, that we can send post cards
OL,18,Ffrom where we've been.
OL,20,F"These dogs have given us independence
OL,21,Fto go places and experience things."
